i xuân nguyên thí bút - 辛亥春元試筆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-6/poem-TsZkU2nkVdDsx-KdZYlTKA">Thường đệ 6 - 裳棣 6</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BB%B1-tr%C3%A0o/poem-Xb2Nkx5fqD34KxYC-LqwHg">Tự trào - 自嘲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-Thi%C3%AAn-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-wlLq6B7jWIy4IAAaknYtNg">Vịnh Đổng Thiên Vương - 詠董天王</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-S%C6%A1n-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-n%C3%AA/poem-Jh0ybTlYkxJlmL_djGuRGg">Vũ (Sơn vũ bất tác nê) - 雨（山雨不作泥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
